# Word-to-Markdown Converter — runtime configuration
#
# Runtime files are ALWAYS stored in the project/app folder that contains
# paths.py / server.py. The fixed layout is:
#
#   <project folder>\Outputs           Converted Markdown (single + batch)
#   <project folder>\Outputs\Images    Extracted images
#   <project folder>\Temp              Short-lived upload scratch
#   <project folder>\Logs              app.log + rotated history
#
# APP_DATA_ROOT is no longer honoured — paths.py pins the runtime root to the
# folder that hosts server.py to keep saves and the UI aligned. Any value set
# here for APP_DATA_ROOT will be ignored at startup.

# Optional GitHub update-check settings. Leave unset for the official repo and
# main branch.
# UPDATE_CHECK_REPOSITORY=fr3dgu1s/Word-to-Markdown-Converter
# UPDATE_CHECK_BRANCH=main
